parameters: \n<Kein>Ah, princess. How nice of you to visit.
\n<\n[1]>Howdy, Kein. How are things around here?
\n<Kein>Booming! This crazy weather has stirred up
the monster population, people are hiring
guards just to get to Castletown, plus
securing the city itself. Business is up!
\n<\n[2]>Never letting a good crisis go to waste,
providing an important service, and if
that happens to benefit the Guild too,
\n<Kein>Anyway, if you're heading in to the storm,
hire a guard or two. I know you and I don't
see eye to eye, but I wouldn't feel right
letting a couple of kids out there on their
\n<Kein>own. You're probably gonna need the extra
First gives hunt to kill Wirewolf boss as a test.
Once that's considered killed,  opens up more hunt quests
